OL,5,G1955 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe week's final visit is to Simon
OL,7,     Fand Lana's lodges in Yorkshire,
OL,8,     Fwhere the hosts pride themselves
OL,9,     Fon luxury. But one guest compares
OL,10,     Fthe place to a caravan park...
OL,11,G2025 Four in a Bed
OL,12,     FOn payment day, the B&Bers take
OL,13,     Feach other to task on everything
OL,14,     Ffrom insufficient slumber to
OL,15,     Fhopeless hosting, before we find
OL,16,     Fout who's won the week.
